title: Safe and Cozy Hostel Room, 1 person, Manhattan
location: Room in Manhattan, New York, United States
description: Just 2 blocks away from Penn Station, MSG and walking distance to Times Square, we offer guests a safe place to rest a stone’s throw away from all the city has to offer.We provide single occupancy rooms with open ceiling and lockable doors. Shared bathrooms include lockable shower doors, shampoo, shower gel and hairdryers.Continental Breakfast, WIFI, & towels are provided24/7 on-site staffThe spaceEach room has a single platform bed (75'' long and 45'' wide) and is intended for single occupancy only. The space includes a bed-side desk, shelf and a power outlet. There is luggage storage space underneath the bed. Shared bathrooms include lockable shower doors,  free shampoo, shower gel and hairdryers. Towels are included in the room but additional towels can be requested. We recommend bringing flip-flops.Guest accessAccess to common areas, with comfy chairs, and desks for remote working.Common facilities include microwaves, fridge, iron & board.To ensure quality sleep, we do provide ear plugs, white noise sound machines, and nasal strips for guests if needed.During your stay24/7 staff on-siteFront desk is open from 7AM to midnightAirbnb messenger is actively managedAsk for our guides to the city (including restaurants for vegans & vegetarians)Volunteer with our staff at Soup KitchenOther things to noteYour stay helps us fund our soup kitchen in the East Village. Many of our guest have supported us feeding the homeless by volunteering their time.Registration DetailsExempt
